      "message": "I don\u0027t feel strongly about how the parameters are grouped. If you both prefer grouping inputFP with success that\u0027s ok by me.\n\nHowever, I do wonder if this is oh so close to:\n using MakeResult \u003d std::tuple\u003cstd::u_p\u003cGrFP\u003e, bool\u003e\n MakeResult Make(std::u_p\u003cGrFP\u003e, ...);\n\nI have a slight personal pref. for tuple returns over out params. It still feel like the caller has enough \"pressure\" to check success/failure.",
